      • eleExtendedFields

        public org.w3c.dom.Document eleExtendedFields
        If YFS_Line_Charges table is extended, then the extended fields are passed as attributes in eleExtendedFields. The XML in this field will be like <LineCharge><Extn Extn1=" "/></LineCharge>, where Extn1 is an extended column.
